What do I do then?

284
00:14:55,888 --> 00:14:57,288
You haven't even won her over yet.

285
00:14:57,377 --> 00:14:59,400
And you're already
hoping she'll get divorced.

286
00:14:59,561 --> 00:15:00,520
Jun,

287
00:15:00,561 --> 00:15:02,241
