291
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,920
No, I can't bear to hurt her.

292
00:15:11,533 --> 00:15:12,800
I'm going to win her back.

293
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:14,680
With my own hands and my own brains,

294
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,321
