463
00:23:50,081 --> 00:23:50,561
Okay.

464
00:23:53,155 --> 00:23:54,320
Thanks. I hope you're right.

465
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:12,720
What are you doing?

466
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,801
What are you doing?

467
00:24:24,841 --> 00:24:26,440
